  [Text] Pyongyang, January 21 (KCNA) -- The U.S. 
imperialists brought overseas-based fighter-bombers, 
pursuit-assault planes, VTOL [vertical take-off and landing] 
assault planes and tanker planes to the air above Wonju, Kunsan, 
Yongwol and Pyongchang, South Korea, on January 18 and 19 to 
