tactical reconnaissance planes and on the 20th an aerial 
reconnaissance on the North's frontline and coastline areas was 
conducted by eight reconnaissance planes of various types 
including "E-3" and "RC-12". 
  Such acts of war provocation are a grave challenge to the 
detente and peace on the Korean peninsula. 

