is aimed at putting a spoke in the wheel of the DPRK-U.S. talks 
and laying a new high hurdle in the solution of the nuclear 
issue. If they stage the war game, the suspension of the `Team 
Spirit' nuclear war exercises will practically be meaningless 
and a more dangerous situation will be created in Korea." 
  "The South Korean authorities must clearly know that if they 
continue to pursue confrontation and war, turning their back on 
the compatriots desirous of reconciliation and unity, detente 
and peace, they will face a stern judgment by the nation, sooner 
or later," he warned. 

