desperate attempt to get out of the serious crisis. 
  The Kim Yong-sam group, driven to an acute crisis in less 
than one year after its seizure of power, seeks to divert 
elsewhere the attention of the people by a more acute 
North-South confrontation and frantic anti-communist war racket 
and keep its power at whatever cost in reliance upon outside 
forces. 
