Rev. Mun Ik-hwan, a patriotic champion of reunification, at his 
bier. 
  By blocking the South Korean visit of our mourners' group 
under an unreasonable pretext the South Korean rulers revealed 
themselves as the truculent fascist dictators, human scums and 
unprecedented barbarians who took off "civilian" veil, bereft of 
elementary human morality and etiquette, the statement said, and 
went on: 
  "The South Korean `regime', which is still branding the 
