and overseas, will wage a vigorous struggle for the achievement 
of great national unity, highly assessing the proposal of the 
overseas headquarters of Pomminnyon to set this year as a year 
of great national unity for national reunification and launch a 
powerful movement for this unity as an entirely just and timely 
initiative. 
  The present situation urgently demands Pomminnyon smash the 
separatists' acts of confrontation against reunification and 
create a favorable climate for reunification in the 1990s, the 
reporter said, proposing measures to that end. 
  He called for vigorously waging the movement for great 
national unity in hearty response to "10-point programme of the 
