Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, January 25 (KCNA) -- The dear leader 
Comrade Kim Chong-il sent messages of greetings to Mohamed 
Abdelaziz, president of the Saharan Arab Democratic Republic and 
secretary general of the Polisario [Popular Front for the 
